{"word":"κνυζηθμός","slug":"κνυζηθμός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n58226\" key=\"knuzhqmo/s\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">κνυζ-ηθμός</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ὁ</gen>, prop. of dogs, <sense id=\"n58226.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">whining, whimpering</tr_>, opp. barking or snarling, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">κύνες τε ἴδον καί ῥ᾽ οὐχ ὑλάοντο, κνυζηθμῷ δ᾽ ἑτέρωσε διὰ σταθμοῖο φόβηθεν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:16:163\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">16.163</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; of wild beasts, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0001.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:884\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.R.\">A.R.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.884</biblScope> </bibl>; of young bears, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0024.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:169\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Opp.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">C.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.169</biblScope> </bibl> (pl.); of children, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0008.tlg001.perseus-grc1:9:376a\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ath.\">Ath.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.376a</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}